At first you have to see the moving objects around you in Slow-Mo.
Try to react on some of the movement.
Play the games which exshaust's your body and also have very less time to react. For example: Football, Table-Tennis, Air-Hockey,etc, but not Mobile and PC games.
Then, you try to emit heat from your starting of back, and then you have to try to transfer that heat to your 1.Arms, 2.Head, 3.Legs.
You will feel something different when sweat will come out, also you will feel you are sweating less than before.
Try to make your reaction time of your body very very very less. 
